176
00:16:21,838 --> 00:16:23,138
Pareço velha?

177
00:16:23,926 --> 00:16:25,262
Cala a boca!

178
00:16:29,746 --> 00:16:31,046
Deixe-me ver.

179
00:16:50,352 --> 00:16:51,686
Certo, pessoal.

180
00:16:54,441 --> 00:16:55,929
Eu vigio primeiro.

181
00:16:56,697 --> 00:16:57,997
Boa noite, Van.

182
00:17:02,311 --> 00:17:03,991
